<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> with scrubbers and other technology, coal burning generating plants are not nearly as toxic as the potential of a nuclear fission powered thermal electric plant.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
